### ✅ Create a New Post
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "content": "This is my first post!"
}

### ✅ Get All Posts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat/posts

### ✅ Update a Post
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/chat/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "content": "Updated post content."
}

### ✅ Add a Comment to a Post
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "userId": 2,
  "content": "Nice post!"
}

### ✅ Get Comments for a Post
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat/comments/1

### ✅ Update a Comment
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/chat/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "commentId": 1,
  "content": "Updated comment text."
}

### ✅ Send a Direct Message
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": 1,
  "receiverId": 2,
  "content": "am good ?"
}

### ✅ Reply to a Direct Message
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages/reply
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": 2,
  "receiverId": 1,
  "content": "I'm doing well! How about you?",
  "parentMessageId": 1
}

### ✅ Get Unread Messages for a User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages/unread/2

### ✅ Mark a Message as Read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages/read/1

### ✅ Get Conversation Between Two Users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages/1/2




### ✅ Delete a Post
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/chat/posts/1

### ✅ Delete a Comment
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/chat/comments/1

### ✅ Delete Messages Between Two Users
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages/1/2

### ✅ Delete Old Messages (Older than 36 Hours)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/chat/messages/old
